title: Breaking Bad All Bad Things (Season 1-5 recap)
description:
I uploaded this issue yesterday and it was missing pages. I got the torrent deleted as soon as I could, but sorry to those that got a an incomplete issue. Please delete it and get this one. I checked and triple checked to make sure all the pages are here. I read it and it flows.

The series finale is tonight so get a refresher on what's happened over the course of the series. This is a 20-page comic that focuses on all the broad strokes. It's also well drawn and written.

I got this from AMC's web site: http://www.amctv.com/shows/breaking-bad/all-bad-things

It's a pain to navigate through so I got all the images and turned them into a cbr. Enjoy.
